OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:
OL,6,FUnsettled to round out the bank
OL,7,Fholiday weekend, cloudier than
OL,8,Frecently, with some rain or showers,
OL,9,Fbut still some brighter weather. Still
OL,10,Fchangeable, but breezier and markedly
OL,11,Fcooler on Tuesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
